<p>Start giving and receiving great gifts by inviting your friends and family to join you on The Wedding Regsitry from other social networks or from your smartphone’s address book.</p>
<br />


<div class="about">Create Personal Gift Registries</div>
<p>The Wedding Registry keeps all of your registry items (Bridal shower, Baby shower, Stag and Doe) together in one place and shares them with only the contacts you specify.</P>

