<div class="script">Get It To Go</div>
<p>Add items on the go, manage your shopping list from anywhere, invite friends using your smartphone’s address book, scan bar codes, take pictures of things you like from the stores you like - all of this is available with The Wedding Registry for your BlackBerry, Android or iPhone.</p>

